<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ rwḥ ạlḥq</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yạrwḥ ạlḥq tʿạl ʿly ạ̹ny ạnạdy lk yạ rwḥ ạlḥq tʿạl ạ̹ly ạ̹ny ạ̉nạdy lk
 yạrwḥ ạlḥq tʿạl ạ̹ly ạ̹ny mḥtạj lk tʿạl ạ̹ly̱ qrby tʿạl wạgẖmrny
 fạnt tḥyny tḥy nfsy ạlʿṭsẖh fạ̉nt trạfqny trạfq wḥdty
 fạ̉nt rfyqy wạnt mrsẖdy</lyrics>
<hymn_number>6960</hymn_number>
<author>mạrk mlky, mạrk mlky</author>
</song>